# Project-local pnpm/npm config.
# Uses the Lilly Artifactory npm mirror for local dev (works behind the Zscaler proxy).
# The repo is designed to work with the public npm registry too — set that with:
#   pnpm config set registry https://registry.npmjs.org/
# for downstream / CI use.
registry=https://elilillyco.jfrog.io/artifactory/api/npm/Lilly-NPM/
